flowchart LR
    DATA[Data Asset]

    DATA --> CLASS{classification}
    CLASS -->|PUBLIC| PUB[no encryption required]
    CLASS -->|INTERNAL| INT[TLS in transit\nAES-256 at rest]
    CLASS -->|CONFIDENTIAL| CONF[TLS + payload encryption\nfield-level masking in logs]
    CLASS -->|RESTRICTED| RESTR[E2E encryption\nHSM key management\nzero-retention logs]

    RESTR --> AUDIT[every access logged + alerted]
    CONF --> AUDIT
